comments: Embiid (PHI) has his arm extended into DeRozan's (CHI) path and makes contact with his arm, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Curry (PHI) extends his arm out and makes clean ball contact on his steal attempt during LaVine's (CHI) drive.
After the pick, Thybulle (PHI) and Ball (CHI) engage and disengage and the contact is marginal.
Thybulle (PHI) maintains a legal guarding position on LaVine (CHI) at the end of the drive and LaVine loses control of the ball on his gather. Embiid (PHI) avoids any contact with LaVine.
Thybulle (PHI) extends his arm and continues to move into Caruso's (CHI) path, affecting Caruso's ability to disengage and contest the shot attempt.
Vucevic (CHI) establishes himself in a screening position in Niang's (PHI) path and absorbs the contact.
Curry (PHI) briefly grasps Vucevic's (CHI) jersey and the contact is marginal as it does not affect his ability to make his intended pass.
Ball (CHI) makes marginal contact with Curry (PHI) on the perimeter.

Thybulle (PHI) firms up with his arm in a vertical position to contest DeRozan's (CHI) jump shot attempt. Any marginal contact after the release is initiated by DeRozan slightly extending his leg away from Thybulle.
Ball (CHI) moves alongside Curry (PHI) with a resting forearm to his side and marginal contact occurs, which does not affect Curry's ability to make his intended pass.
Curry (PHI) loses his balance as he retrieves the off-target pass and Ball (CHI) avoids contact on his steal attempt at the start of the drive.
Caruso (CHI) legally contests Curry's (PHI) jump shot attempt.

Replay review of the foul called on Embiid (PHI) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. Embiid makes clean ball contact to block DeRozan's (CHI) driving shot attempt and any follow-through contact after the block is deemed incidental.
Caruso (CHI) commits a take foul on Maxey (PHI).
Vucevic (CHI) establishes himself in a screening position in Thybulle's (PHI) path and absorbs the contact.
